com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi

Class LucentEndpointUnregisteredReason

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.LucentEndpointUnregisteredReason

  • public class LucentEndpointUnregisteredReason
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the possible reasons an H.323 or SIP endpoint has unregistered.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static short UR_AUDIT_FAILURE
      A CM audit has detected a problem with the endpoint.
      static short UR_CALL_EXPIRED
      The call preservation timer for the endpoint has expired.
      static short UR_DCP_STN_STATE
      The endpoint is an IP soft phone in a shared control configuration with a DCP telephone, and the soft phone is no longer in a valid state.
      static short UR_EXTENSION_REMOVED
      The extension where the endpoint was registered has been removed.
      static short UR_FORCE_LOGIN
      The endpoint was unregistered to allow a different endpoint to register at the same extension.
      static short UR_INVALID_STATE
      The endpoint is in an invalid state.
      static short UR_LOGOFF
      The user logged off at the endpoint.
      static short UR_LOST_SIGNALING_CONNECTION
      The signaling connection has been lost for this endpoint.
      static short UR_MODULE_ID_MISMATCH
      Module ID mismatch.
      static short UR_NO_H323_CONNECTION
      CM received a keep alive request from a dual connect endpoint whose H.323 extension is not registered.
      static short UR_NO_LAN_PORTS
      CM has run out of LAN port IDs.
      static short UR_NO_SIGNALLING_CONNECTION
      The signaling connection between CM and the endpoint has been lost.
      static short UR_OTHER
      A more specific reason cannot be provided.
      static short UR_Q931_TIMEOUT
      CM did not receive a Q.931 SETUP message from the endpoint after it registered.
      static short UR_REGISTRATION_EXPIRED
      The endpoint's link loss delay timer has expired.
      static short UR_REMOTE_MAX_MTC
      The endpoint is a Remote Max station that is undergoing maintenance.
      static short UR_RO_TT_MTC
      A background maintenance task has requested the removal of Remote Office LAN Terminal Translation Initialization (TTI) ports.
      static short UR_SAT_COMMAND
      A SAT command to unregister all H.323 endpoints has been invoked.
      static short UR_SHARED_CONTROL
      The endpoint is an IP soft phone in a shared control configuration with an IP telephone, and the telephone has unregistered.
      static short UR_SHARED_CONTROL_MTC
      The endpoint is a shared control soft phone that is maintenance busy.
      static short UR_SIGNALLING_CONNECTION_CLOSED
      The signaling connection for the endpoint has been closed.
      static short UR_SOFTPHONE
      The IP Softphone setting for the extension where the endpoint was registered has been changed from 'y' to 'n'.
      static short UR_STATION_MTC
      The SAT commands 'busyout station' and 'release station' have been invoked for the station extension where the endpoint was registered.
      static short UR_SYSTEM_RESTART
      A system restart was initiated just after the endpoint registered.
      static short UR_TSA
      The endpoint is an IP soft phone in a shared control configuration, and the user has entered telephone self administration mode.
      static short UR_UR_TTL_EXPIRED
      The endpoint's time to live has expired without CM receiving a keep alive registration request.
